attributes.long-description:
Drive Dom Toretto's Dodge Ice Charger from The Fate of the Furious™, his iconic 1970 Dodge Charger R/T from the film that launched the epic Fast & Furious™ saga, and Brian O'Conner's 1999 Nissan Skyline GT-R R34 from 2 Fast 2 Furious™. Each car comes with Wheels and six unique Decals.

1-4 players
Network Players 2-8
100MB minimum save size
DUALSHOCK®4
Remote Play
Online Play (Optional)

Software subject to license (us.playstation.com/softwarelicense). Online features require an account and are subject to terms of service and applicable privacy policy (playstationnetwork.com/terms-of-service & playstationnetwork.com/privacy-policy). One-time license fee for play on account’s designated primary PS4™ system and other PS4™ systems when signed in with that account.

WARNING: The driving sequences in the motion picture Fast & Furious™ were filmed with professional stunt drivers, under carefully-controlled conditions, for entertainment purposes only. No attempt should be made to duplicate any of the racing activities or sequences depicted therein.
